!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}/
    :css
      *{
      padding: 0px;
      margin: 0px;
      }
  %body
    .wrapper{style: "padding: 30px 0px; font-family:arial"}
      %table{style: "margin: 0 auto;max-width: 677px;width: 100%; font-family:arial;margin-top: 50px;padding: 12px 12px;"}
        %tbody
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 10px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              ="Hi #{@answer.ticket.asker_firstname},"
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 10px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              Your question has been answered!
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 10px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              = @answer.try(:user).try(:first_name)
              has answered with:
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              =sanitize @answer.content
          %tr
            %td{style: "text-align: center;padding-top: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;"}
              =link_to 'Click Here to Reply', issue_url(@answer.ticket), style: "background: #009348; border: 1px solid #00813f; border-radius: 5px; color: #ffffff; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 27px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none;font-size: 15px; font-family:arial;", class: 'btn_visit'
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 24px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              Kind regards,
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 34px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              GradReady Student Success Team
          %tr
            %td{style: "color: #808080; font-size: 13px;"}
              %i Please note that replies to this email are not monitored; if you would like to amend or submit a response to your support ticket, please do so by clicking on the above link and following the prompts.
